attachments.title: Max2 Inc. - Android Software Engineer
attachments.text: ABOUT US We are Max2 Inc. - the makers of the Scene apps (<http://www.sceneapp.io>). Scene is a community powered discovery platform for getting real-time knowledge about local venues and retail offers. There are plenty of review sites already out there, our app will bridge the gap by providing a comprehensive end-to-end solution with cutting edge devices and technologies for users and merchants. Max2 is an equal opportunity employer. DESCRIPTION We are looking for an experienced Android engineer to join our development team who has a passion for delivering great mobile user experiences and working through complex problems. Candidates should have strong but well-founded opinions on code style, structure, automated processes and product building, and should like to sweat over every little detail while being able to iterate quickly.

text: Hi All, I'm with Carrot, We are a startup working to humanize the job search experience for individuals with high demand technical skill-sets.  Any suggestions on which channel is best to solicit feedback?  Here's a taste of what we're doing <https://carrotcareers.com/companies/osmo/teams/osmo-product> Thank you.

attachments.title: Build it
attachments.text: We work at the forefront of how people interact with technology. It's fascinating to build technology products for children. Getting to see their facial expressions and how they interact with our product. They're so authentic, direct and passionate. It inspires us to really push the boundaries, but also keeps us grounded. Osmo is a groundbreaking product that is recognized worldwide for its innovation in technology for kids. There are serious technical challenges in what we do and there is so much more we can do. If working for a company that has a noble sense of purpose, that's backed by of one of the world's most acclaimed investors (Accel) and getting to work on the cutting edge of technology gets your passions flowing, you might be the right fit to join Osmo's team. We'd love to connect with you.
